      <p class="article-subtitle">Epictetus spent years as a slave, had his leg deliberately broken by his master, and went on to teach a philosophy of radical inner freedom — the most powerful idea about control ever articulated.</p>
      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person" style="display:none">
        <span itemprop="name">{author}</span>
      </span>
    </header>

