      <ol>
        <li><a href="#who-was-epictetus">Who Was Epictetus?</a></li>
        <li><a href="#dichotomy">The Dichotomy of Control</a></li>
        <li><a href="#what-is-up-to-us">What Is and Is Not Up to Us</a></li>
